This is the protocol for a review and there is no abstract. The objectives are as follows:, Primary objective:, To determine the efficacy and safety of alpha-2 adrenergic agonists for reducing mortality and cardiovascular complications following cardiac and non-cardiac surgery., Secondary objectives:, (1) To compare the efficacy and safety of clonidine, mivazerol, and dexmedetomidine for reducing mortality and cardiovascular complications following cardiac and non-cardiac surgery., (2) To compare the efficacy and safety of alpha-2 adrenergic agonists for reducing mortality and cardiovascular complications following cardiac, vascular non-cardiac, and non-vascular non-cardiac surgery